### Snap pick to body center:
funckey F14 "prepopup; pop dyn_option_select 'Snap pick to@:@Symbol Center'"

### Snap pick to segment vertex:
funckey F15 "prepopup; pop dyn_option_select 'Snap pick to@:@Segment Vertex'"

### Snap pick to segment midpoint:
funckey SF15 "prepopup; pop dyn_option_select 'Snap pick to@:@Segment Midpoint'"

### Snap pick to pin:
funckey F16 "prepopup; pop dyn_option_select 'Snap pick to@:@Pin'"
### Snap pick to pad edge midpoint:
funckey SF16 "prepopup; pop dyn_option_select 'Snap pick to@:@Pad Edge Midpoint'"
funckey f "prepopup; pop dyn_option_select 'Snap pick to@:@Pad Edge Midpoint'"

### Snap pick to intersection:
funckey F17 "prepopup; pop dyn_option_select 'Snap pick to@:@Segment Intersection'"

### Snap pick to arc center:
funckey sF17 "prepopup; pop dyn_option_select 'Snap pick to@:@Arc/Circle Center'"


